  "title": "CHEF",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>- Oversee all kitchen operations, including food preparation, cooking, and presentation, ensuring top-quality standards and consistency.</p>\n<p>- Design and develop menus (including mixed rice/economic rice menu planning), highlighting authentic Chinese and live seafood specialties while staying current with culinary trends.</p>\n<p>- Must have experience in planning mixed rice/economy rice menus, with the ability to create diverse and cost-effective mixed rice meal sets.</p>\n<p>- Manage food costs, inventory, and procurement to maximize profitability without compromising quality.</p>\n<p>- Strictly adhere to food hygiene, safety, and workplace health regulations, maintaining a clean and organized kitchen.</p>\n<p>- Lead, train, and motivate the kitchen team, fostering a collaborative and positive work environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Minimum 5 years of experience in Chinese cuisine and live seafood, including mixed rice/economy rice operations.</p>\n<p>- Proven ability in mixed rice menu planning, with expertise in designing varied and cost-efficient meal sets.</p>\n<p>- Strong skills in menu creation, recipe development, and culinary innovation.</p>\n<p>- Valid food hygiene certification.</p>\n<p>- Excellent leadership and team management abilities.</p>\n<p>- Proficient in food cost control and kitchen budgeting.</p>\n<p>- Fluent in Mandarin (spoken) with basic English reading/writing skills.</p>\n<p>- Willing to work 6 days a week, 12-hour shifts (including weekends/public holidays).</p>",
